data.description: This stunning 2-story 4 bedroom, 2.5 bath is a perfect blend of modern elegance & country charm. Situated on 2.66 acres, offering the quietness of rural living with the convenience of urban amenities. The front entrance leads you into a light filled home featuring hardwood floors & large windows that showcase the views of the surrounding landscape. All 4 bedrooms, 2 full bathrooms, & laundry area can be found on the 2nd floor, allowing plenty of space for a growing family or accommodating guests on the main level.  This home has a 2 car attached garage, a detached garage, a double carport, ample parking, & a storage shed. A small greenhouse adds a touch of green thumb charm, located just off the detached garage and a few steps away from the pre-existing large garden area. Enjoy the outdoors on the covered patio just off the living room, perfect for entertaining or unwinding while taking in the scenic views of your expansive backyard. Contact Paige Eustice at 270-871-3333 for more info.
